message.body: I'm so sad and sorry that we didn't connect new year's eve. when do you go back to philly?
Next Sunday, but I may be able to see you this wednesday, not sure though. My dad has surgery so I'll be around but in a hospital and whatever. I'm supposed to stop at meg's though so we'll see...
lions and tigers and bitches oh my! there's no place like a winter premier. see you there. --a
